Update Journal Entry for Juror 4 (Averik)

I have spoken with Averik, a vile and despicable man who unfortunately also happens to be a juror in Rolgan's case.  Averik readily believes the stereotypes of the drunken, heathen Uthgardt savage, and I will want to avoid encouraging them during the trial.  However, I suspect this disgusting excuse for a man could be strongly swayed by Vanda's testimony - he seems strongly attracted to her.
